com.interpss.core.aclf.adj

Interface RemoteQBus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfControlBus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, PVBusLimit
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StaticVarCompensator, SwitchedShunt
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RemoteQBusImpl, StaticVarCompensatorImpl, SwitchedShuntImpl

    public interface RemoteQBus
extends PVBusLimit
    A representation of the model object 'Remote QBus'. Remote Q voltage control bus class - use the parent bus Q to control the voltage of a remote bus or reactive power through a remote branch. The parent bus should be a regular gen PQ bus. The remote bus could be this bus itself, can not be a GenPV or Swing bus. RemoteQBus id is the same as the busId of this bus.

    The following features are supported:

    • Control Type
    • Flow From2 To
    • Mvar On From Side
    • DQ dv
    • Acc Factor
    • Remote Bus
    • Remote Branch
    See Also:
    AclfAdjustPackage.getRemoteQBus()
